title: Not able to patch 6.14
body:
Hey guys, I checked the FAQ at the head of the fourm, but it did not work for me. It stops at 2-3% an says "Unspecified Error, check logs for details" I also pulled up my cmd and pinged google to see if my internet was going out, but it was fine the whole time.

replies.body: It sounds like the patcher may have been blocked from scanning files due to a [permissions ](https://support.riotgames.com/hc/en-us/articles/204134104-Setting-up-your-Permissions)issue.  I'm glad to hear everything is okay now!  Best of luck on the rift!
Glad you got it to work, good luck on the Fields of Justice!
